    <releaseNotes>
    - New: Add a button to clear the current virtual library easily
    - New: Driver for Surftab Ventos
    - New: Ebook-viewer: Allow re-ordering bookmarks in the bookmarks manager by drag and drop.
    - Fixed: DOCX Input: Fix conversion breaking for files that use heading style paragraphs to insert line rules
    - Fixed: Content server: Fix last search query not being fully sanitized in results page
    - Fixed: Book polishing: Fix page margins being removed if an unused font was found during subsetting of embedded fonts.
    - Fixed: PDF Output: Do not error out when the input document uses a font that cannot be subset, such as the Symbol font. Instead print a warning and embed the full font.
    - Fixed: Conversion: Fix a regression in the last release that broke conversion of a few files with comments just before a chapter start.
	- New News Source: Blindbuch and No names, No jackets by Armin Geller
	- New News Source: El Tribuno Salta and Jujuy by Darko Miletic
    - Improved News Source: Something Awful
	- Improved News Source: Spektrum der Wissenschaft
	- Improved News Source: mediapart.fr
	- Improved News Source: Dilbert
	- Improved News Source: Antyweb
	- Improved News Source: Scientific American
	- Improved News Source: taz.de (RSS)
    </releaseNotes>
